      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 0,
          "text": "One dollar and eighty-seven cents was all the money that Della had saved.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 1,
          "text": "That was everything she had after saving for months.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 2,
          "text": "Della counted her money again, but it was still only one dollar and eighty-seven cents.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 3,
          "text": "She wanted to buy Jim a special Christmas gift.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_0.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 1,
      "bundleId": "bundle_1",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 4,
          "text": "Christmas was coming tomorrow, and she felt desperate about the money situation.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 5,
          "text": "She sat down on her old couch and started crying softly.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 6,
          "text": "She loved Jim very much and wanted to make him happy.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 7,
          "text": "He worked hard every day at his office job.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_1.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 2,
      "bundleId": "bundle_2",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 8,
          "text": "She desperately wanted to find something special and meaningful for him.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 9,
          "text": "But she had no money left after paying all their bills.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 10,
          "text": "She walked to the mirror and looked at her reflection carefully.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 11,
          "text": "Her beautiful hair was very long and reached her waist gracefully.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_2.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 3,
      "bundleId": "bundle_3",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 12,
          "text": "It was thick, shiny brown hair that everyone always admired.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 13,
          "text": "Suddenly she had a brilliant idea about selling her precious hair.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 14,
          "text": "She knew that women sometimes sold their hair to make money.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 15,
          "text": "She quickly put on her winter coat and rushed outside.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_3.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 4,
      "bundleId": "bundle_4",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 16,
          "text": "She hurried down the street until she found a shop that bought hair.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 17,
          "text": "The woman in the shop examined her hair and bought it immediately.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 18,
          "text": "Della received twenty dollars for her beautiful hair, which was enough money.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 19,
          "text": "Now she finally had enough money to buy Jim's Christmas present.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_4.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 5,
      "bundleId": "bundle_5",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 20,
          "text": "She felt both happy and sad about losing her beautiful hair.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 21,
          "text": "Her lovely hair was completely gone, and she looked very different without it.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 22,
          "text": "She went shopping to find the perfect gift for her husband.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 23,
          "text": "She discovered a beautiful platinum watch chain in an elegant jewelry store.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_5.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 6,
      "bundleId": "bundle_6",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 24,
          "text": "It was absolutely perfect for Jim's precious gold pocket watch that he treasured.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 25,
          "text": "Jim loved his grandfather's gold watch more than anything else he owned.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 26,
          "text": "The expensive chain cost exactly twenty dollars, which was all her money.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 27,
          "text": "She bought the beautiful chain for Jim without any hesitation.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_6.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 7,
      "bundleId": "bundle_7",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 28,
          "text": "She returned home with the special gift and felt nervous about Jim's reaction.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 29,
          "text": "She was very worried about how Jim would react to her short hair.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 30,
          "text": "What would Jim think when he saw her completely different appearance?",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 31,
          "text": "She prepared their dinner carefully and waited anxiously for him to come home.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_7.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 8,
      "bundleId": "bundle_8",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 32,
          "text": "Jim came home from work and stopped suddenly when he saw her.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 33,
          "text": "He looked at Della with a strange, surprised expression on his face.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 34,
          "text": "He immediately noticed her short hair and seemed shocked by the dramatic change.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 35,
          "text": "He was completely surprised and couldn't believe what he was seeing.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_8.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 9,
      "bundleId": "bundle_9",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 36,
          "text": "Della nervously explained why she had sold her precious hair for money.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 37,
          "text": "She proudly showed him the beautiful platinum watch chain she had bought.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 38,
          "text": "Jim looked at her with a sad but loving smile on his face.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 39,
          "text": "He told her that he also had a special surprise for her.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_9.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 10,
      "bundleId": "bundle_10",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 40,
          "text": "He had sold his precious watch earlier that day to buy something special.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 41,
          "text": "He had bought beautiful decorative combs for her long, lovely hair.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 42,
          "text": "The expensive combs were specifically designed for her beautiful long hair that was now gone.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 43,
          "text": "Now both of their thoughtful gifts were completely useless to each other.",
          "startTime": 6,
          "endTime": 8
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_10.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 8
    },
    {
      "bundleIndex": 11,
      "bundleId": "bundle_11",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 44,
          "text": "But they realized that they loved each other more than ever before.",
          "startTime": 0,
          "endTime": 2
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 45,
          "text": "The gifts had shown their true, deep love and sacrifice for each other.",
          "startTime": 2,
          "endTime": 4
        },
        {
          "sentenceIndex": 46,
          "text": "They were truly the wisest and most loving people in the world.",
          "startTime": 4,
          "endTime": 6
        }
      ],
      "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/gift-of-the-magi/A2/sarah/bundle_11.mp3",
      "totalDuration": 6
    }
